author: supun
msg: SAML 1.1 Assertion and Protocol implementation for RampartC. SAML implementation uses the Axiom object model. Special thanks goes to Prasad Perera for implementing SAML protocol and SAML Signature.

author: rse
msg: Use plain "apr_time_now" for seeding the PRNG instead of using
unnecessarily destroys entropy and performs unnecessary additional
calculation (because of resolution adjustments which are UUID-related
and hence are of no interest for PRNG seeding at all).
